import { AppBar, Box, Link, List, ListItemText, Toolbar, Typography } from "@mui/material"
import FoodBankIcon from '@mui/icons-material/FoodBank';

function Navbar() {
    return (
        <>
            <Box>
                <AppBar>
                    <Toolbar>
                        <Typography
                          color={'white'} 
                          variant="h6"
                          component='div'
                          sx={{flexGrow:1}}
                        >
                            <FoodBankIcon sx={{mt:4}}/>
                            Al-Baik
                        </Typography>
                        <Box>
                            <List sx={{bgcolor:"black",display:"flex"}}>
                                <ListItemText>
                                    <Link to={'/'}>Home</Link>
                                </ListItemText>
                                <ListItemText>
                                    <Link to={'/menu'}>Menu</Link>
                                </ListItemText>
                                <ListItemText>
                                    <Link to={'/about'}>About</Link>
                                </ListItemText>
                                <ListItemText>
                                    <Link to={'/contact'}>Contact</Link>
                                </ListItemText>



                            </List>
                        </Box>
                    </Toolbar>
                </AppBar>
            </Box>
        </>
    )
}

export default Navbar
